How it work

A better, smarter currency can be used by anyone, anywhere, anytime.

Crypteck is a stable, decentralized currency that does not discriminate. Any individual or business can realize the advantages of digital money.

  • It is able to fully benefit from Ethereum’s network effects
  • It is inherently more secure
  • It is more open and powerful

Total control with our transaction system

Transaction system will never ask you for your wallet keys. Your funds will be securely held on a public listed blockchain within a uniquely created keyless smart contract.

our story

our concept & mission

In April 2017, Crypteck was launched by Eric Vander and Jane Mobasser with the intention to solve blockchain finance for all. The goal was to bring mobile apps to the masses and create a platform that enabled a brand to design, launch and manage an app with no coding or development work required.

Digital Assets

You can easily create digital assets to better monetize traditional financial instruments, gain access to a global investor audience, and improve liquidity.

Decentralized Finance

DeFi is a new financial system that allows everyone to earn money in new ways globally. With DeFi, anyone in the world can use all the financial tools.

Tokenized Real Estate

Digitalization and fractionalization of real estate make secondary markets more liquid and attract new investors, better access to real estate investments for individuals.
